\section{Conclusion}
%% ============================================================

The resulting framework unifies nonlinear dynamics, control, lattice
path geometry, and finite-state verification into a single specification.
The global envelope law $M_{\min}=(1+C_\phi)\,\phi_{\mathrm{peak}}
+C_r\,r_{\mathrm{peak}}$ provides a parametric design tool for
verification models.

